{"tid":1391794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]點樣防止義士被捕","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:51:25.000Z","uid":58555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e10c324158813a983a6a3888fbbac24083282a8e","tid":1391794,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySHmxME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySHmxME.png&h=de4b5cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隔離唔好當前線係乞衣post度偷返嚟<br />\n<br />\n到咗今日 示威者嘅技巧應該係進步先係<br />\n大家反思吓點解會愈嚟愈多義士被捕<br />\n同集思廣益吓<span style=\"color: red;\">如何防止前線義士被捕</span><br />\n睇返幾個被捕義士上報嘅post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5E8cOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5E8cOw.png&h=abd527e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n縱火、管有爆炸品、意圖造成身體嚴重傷害罪係最高刑罰<br />\n我本人有少少建議 睇下義士們啱唔啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線義士可以用<span style=\"color: red;\">接力形式</span><br />\n一個hit完到下個 hit完真係要run <br />\n防止設完路障等等俾狗周到嘅機會<br />\n義士做危險性愈高嘅行動愈要手足保護<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 想問喺黑警手上扯返手足返嚟嘅可行性大唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4873c08c9f0fcc2dae9679f5e81df244ae99cd7","tid":1391794,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ad933831cd60a063aaa87ac701ede733a759b4","tid":1391794,"uid":58555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdcf80f714d2375fa7da95c6d228e3f118cf147","tid":1391794,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:21:24.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br